香港人既抗爭熱潮冷卻咗落嚟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋近1000個手足被捕<br />\n3人盲眼<br />\n1人腳部被斬至永久傷殘<br />\n1人被斬至肺功能受損<br />\n<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日忽然見到好多帶風向post<br />\n話聽日要入機場<br />\n<br />\n好老實講<br />\n經過2星期和理非<br />\n個社會好似唔記得晒警察 政府點殘暴對待市民<br />\n連政府高官 權貴eg 曾俊華都吹和風<br />\n想香港人妥協<br />\n<br />\n所以我好多謝今日觀塘手足既付出<br />\n將革命重新延續落去<br />\n聽日對運動嚟講亦係一個關鍵<br />\n究竟革命能否延續<br />\n就睇各位放唔放棄"},{"pid":"8f9216c61709fb0b985166f6f20d25c020a62a5f","tid":1502104,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔好再比權貴吹和風<br />\n825 聽日葵芳見<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"171265a76e6404fec751041b4218b0675d2d2375","tid":1502104,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:00:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"0562174770023531c1002865e3f9452b40943613","tid":1502104,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"896cd3a8ebd9e0dd134d2fa39b589d0ba1af64f6","tid":1502104,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span>"},{"pid":"e08e06805c9254041f837aa0b64e55be05e21850","tid":1502104,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"f92f6993df4827e99655ada70eedf214a9910d32","tid":1502104,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6957222952f11d344639f22753fb26a2c3319977","tid":1502104,"uid":2